{"tid":1951824,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企鐵閘裝防盜閉路電視有無問題？","createTime":"2020-03-31T08:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T08:55:54.000Z","uid":50878,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"de7a8a3fb7a23f897419a1724b618f047467ab65","tid":1951824,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"隔離屋果戶人幾十年黎都痴線既<br />\n我細個行過佢見到都打我落地<br />\n<br />\n最近仲癲到想爆開我鐵閘唔知做乜<br />\n我一開門喝止，佢地就好有部署咁入lift 即走<br />\nlift cctv 都影到係佢地<br />\n<br />\n門鈴等等既野都經常比佢地打爆哂所以都無裝<br />\n<br />\n最近佢地越黎越過火<br />\n想裝番個cctv 睇實<br />\n<br />\n一來要夠堅實無咁易比佢拆落黎<br />\n<br />\n二來都想留意番有無違法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打可以教教路等小弟睇下點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33e001e3fdcd639c8bc4532c655e8695bd1491c","tid":1951824,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"752d1e42f1256a13c93b44f22a9c3e7ef8da82e7","tid":1951824,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:14:53.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"8bdee2b362dada9af1c5a16e664c8b9c3502f276","tid":1951824,"uid":346191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:15:31.000Z","msg":"打撚7佢囉 咪佢唔識驚"},{"pid":"870df70927478540f4081faae187085980528cbf","tid":1951824,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"聽過可以，不過要加塊牌講比人知錄影進行中。<br />\n（淨牌都有阻嚇作用）<br />\n好似係炸"},{"pid":"789e644d4726b21129f72bfc05da9fe41c53e535","tid":1951824,"uid":211204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"公屋？如果係公屋果種趟閘可以係上方條軌尾放個cctv入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地唔會睇到，但可以影哂屋企門口"},{"pid":"7715b7d4642ad93cd38f4a8d6244d084d8719ef6","tid":1951824,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bdee2b362dada9af1c5a16e664c8b9c3502f276","tid":1951824,"uid":346191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":